    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative E46 M3, a purist\u2019s specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS timing. This example delivers linear power delivery to an 8,000 RPM redline, mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement and features a refreshed suspension with Bilstein dampers and OEM bushings to maintain factory-spec kinematics. The exterior retains its original paint depth and luster, while the interior displays immaculate Nappa leather and perfect pixel density on all displays. Mechanically sound with a documented service dossier, this vehicle represents a turnkey investment for the discerning enthusiast.",
