    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-fresh condition, having been meticulously stored in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a professional ceramic coating applied to ensure a mirror-like finish, entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin serves as a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, with no signs of wear or bolster compression. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the adaptive driver-assist features, functions flawlessly. This car has been maintained strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule at a certified dealership, with a comprehensive folder of service records included. It has never seen inclement weather, has never been smoked in, and still carries that distinct new-car scent. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection, this is a rare opportunity to acquire a masterpiece in its prime.",
